ts and more training?\n6.  **Qualitative Analysis:** Dive deeper into *why* the QA-Transformer produces different output. Does it show any signs of improved consistency, factual accuracy, or answerability, even if its general fluency is lower?\n\nThis is a good starting point for exploring novel loss functions to imbue language models with additional capabilities beyond simple next-token prediction. It touches on important research areas in making LLMs more reliable and controllable.\n",
